    <p>{`By default images or videos aren't removed automatically. This means that the Kerberos agent will keep writing to disk, even if there is no more space available on your SD card. When your SD card is full you'll be experiencing strange errors: a corrupt web interface, blank images or corrupt videos.`}</p>
    <p>{`To resolve this your should install a simple bash script and initiate a cronjob which continuously poll your filesystem, and start removing media when your disk is getting full.`}</p>
